      <div class="patch-row"><div class="patch-row-info"><div class="patch-row-label">Main &amp; fallback retry counters + delay</div><div class="patch-row-desc"><strong>Uncheck to remove</strong> the main retry attempts, fallback retry attempts, and retry delay steppers from Settings. Defaults (3 main retries, 3 fallback retries, 3s delay) will be locked in permanently.</div></div><div class="patch-check" data-patch="fallback-retries" data-section="fallback" onclick="togglePatch(this)"></div></div>
